Vegas: Alright, there we go! Flying tank sneak attack, baby! They won’t know what hit ‘em!
Phoenix: I know you two run on it, but please don’t let your hubris blind you…
Phoenix: The whole plan is that they WILL know what hit ‘em. And it seems to be working. Yi’s fleet just took a sharp turn.
Phoenix: Since he took the bait, you don’t actually have to engage with the fleet by the mainland. Once Yi is here, focus all your power on them instead!
Yi: I see… whoever’s commanding you certainly has quite a read on our movements.
Yi: Thankfully, I already accounted for a spy in our midst.
Vegas: Hey… hey, is the sky supposed to be on fire?
Yi: I will no longer be accepting surrender. You are being sunk right here and right now.
Yi: Advance, my flamewall, destroy them! For cardboard! For Felix!
Phoenix: I’m not even worried at this point… do your thing, guys.